": {"login": "antoine2711", "name": "Antoine Beaubien"}}, "url": "https://github.com/OpenRefine/OpenRefine/commit/d26b72bede09774010f50aabcdf63d43d0f25db6", "committedDate": "2020-04-17T08:39:41Z", "message": "Use this._minimizeState instead of this._config.minimize\n\nUse this._minimizeState instead of this._config.minimize to keep track of the minimized state of the facet"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestReview", "id": "MDE3OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Mzk1NTM1MjI1", "url": "https://github.com/OpenRefine/OpenRefine/pull/2558#pullrequestreview-395535225", "createdAt": "2020-04-17T15:05:04Z", "commit": {"oid": "d26b72bede09774010f50aabcdf63d43d0f25db6"}, "state": "APPROVED", "comments": {"totalCount": 0, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": null, "endCursor": null, "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": []}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "f4e6ab92fc3253314904b46cdadf1d5be2df1620", "author": {"user": {"login": "antoine2711", "name": "Antoine Beaubien"}}, "url": "https://github.com/OpenRefine/OpenRefine/commit/f4e6ab92fc3253314904b46cdadf1d5be2df1620", "committedDate": "2020-04-17T20:17:20Z", "message": "Carry the modifications from ListFacet to all other facets\n\n\u2022 Carry the modifications from ListFacet to all RangeFacet, ScatterPlotFacet, TestSearchFacet, TimeRangeFacet.\n\u2022 Also, add the maximize action to the ToolTip.\n\u2022 CleanUp of hierarchie of HTML or Facets."}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "cc150fecfa3b4bda272fd51339be1cc7a1005431", "author": {"user": {"login": "antoine2711", "name": "Antoine Beaubien"}}, "url": "https://github.com/OpenRefine/OpenRefine/commit/cc150fecfa3b4bda272fd51339be1cc7a1005431", "committedDate": "2020-04-17T20:30:34Z", "message": "Update translation-fr.json\n\n\"Permuter la minimisation ou la maximisation de cette facette\""}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "b4278dd70154576dfca617ebfa2d1e7f6f1730e9", "author": {"user": {"login": "antoine2711", "n